definition: to put/to place/to release/to free/to let go/to let out/to set off (fireworks)

sentences.english: The seedlings were placed in a big flat.
sentences.chinese: 秧苗被放置在一大片浅苗床上。

sentences.english: Do not clutter up the page with so many illustrations that you obscure the message.
sentences.chinese: 不要在一页内放置过多的插图，那样会模糊讯息。

sentences.english: The spark plugs on modern bikes are always hard to reach.
sentences.chinese: 火星塞很不好取下，因为放置的太深。

sentences.english: Placing dead bodies in a bone room.
sentences.chinese: 将尸体放置在尸骸存放屋。

sentences.english: The another big characteristic that small family bedroom places furniture is to fore-and-aft development.
sentences.chinese: 小户型居室放置家具的另一大特色就是向纵向发展。

sentences.english: Store in a cool, dry place and kept away from children .
sentences.chinese: 宜放置阴凉干爽及儿童不能接触之处。

sentences.english: Don't put the fermentation container close to potting plants.
sentences.chinese: 发酵容器不能靠近盆栽植物放置。

sentences.english: Light Box must be placed in a dark room or curtained area with out incidental light.
sentences.chinese: 灯箱要放置在暗室或用窗帘罩住不易透光的地方。

sentences.english: This is accomplished by a variety of thoughtfully placed, clerestory windows, skylights and Solatubes.
sentences.chinese: 这是通过各种静心思考放置的天窗，天窗和索乐图。

sentences.english: Then it is left until most of the water dries up.
sentences.chinese: 接着它被放置到大部分的水干了。

sentences.english: It will be located on top of Mauna Kea, Hawaii.
sentences.chinese: 它将会放置在夏威夷莫纳克亚山的顶点。

sentences.english: Several dead bodies lay under the portrait of Mao on Tiananmen Gate.
sentences.chinese: 几具尸体放置在毛之下画象在天安门门。

sentences.english: Place the chicken breast on cutting board, with one sheet of plastic film under it, and cover it with another sheet.
sentences.chinese: 将鸡胸肉放置在砧板上，上下各铺一张保鲜膜。

sentences.english: Today, caskets are usually placed in above-ground-vaults, like the ones pictured here.
sentences.chinese: 现在，如图所示，棺材通常都放置在地上灵堂。

sentences.english: They are placed in the ground about the time of the first frost.
sentences.chinese: 它们被放置在地面的初霜时间。

sentences.english: Place in a dry condition to obtain the best anti- fog effect.
sentences.chinese: 放置于干燥处，以保护镜面防雾效果。
